des: Gorge Country Y102 is the Mid-Columbia's Country leader. Playing today's new country and the country favorites from years gone by. We feature 3 different Classic Country shows, 2 hours of Cowboy tunes and Poetry on Saturday mornings from 6 - 8 am. We begin each morning with the National Anthem at 6 am. Find us at gorgecountry.com. We are a Gorge Country Media station based in The Dalles, Oregon.
